<td bgcolor="#CECECE" class="btext" width="100%"><b>Uncrossable Parallel stuff</b> - <span class=bsmall>posted by  <a class='nNewsMailLink' href='mailto:StealthBuda@barrysworld.com'>StealthBuda</a> on Wed 07 November 2001 07:18:57 | <a href="comments.php?section=4&index=491" class=blink>Comments (0)</a></span></td>
